<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/252216-are-any-of-you-high-school-teachers-how">Are any of you high school teachers? How do you feel about teaching this book at the accelerated sophomore level in school? Or, if you&#39;re a parent, how would you feel about your child reading this at the high school level?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_252216'><a id="like_count_community_question_252216" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/252216?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">7 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F5632446-columbine">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/252216-are-any-of-you-high-school-teachers-how">6 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/252216-are-any-of-you-high-school-teachers-how">See all 12 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
